<h3 id="ma-6-timely-maintenance-m-h">MA-6 Timely Maintenance (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization obtains maintenance support and/or spare parts for [Assignment: organization-defined information system components] within [Assignment: organization-defined time period] of failure.</p>

